commit message: Changed die selection to be on touch up not touch down.
Creating new dice collection for SPDiceView.

Adding touch up inside callback in SPDiceView, and optional selection.

* Classes using SPDiceView can be notified when the user touches up
inside on a die.
* SPDiceView dice selection is now optional.
Adding margin along the screen border.
Showing die sum, and refactoring SPDie's facingValue to facingSide.

Improving dice blender scene.

* Keyframes for each facing value.
* Elongated d8.
Replacing remove with reset because it's more intuitive.
Changing icon background color, and removing overlay.
Making Icon border, and rearranging dice in icon.
Fixing bug where available dice were spread apart too much.
Animating banner ad entry and exit.
Moving ad banner to the top.
Fixing ad banner not disappearing properly.
Scaling and centering of D10x10 numbers.
Automating background copying from renders to assets.
Adding other icon sizes to the plist metadata.
Updating credits screen content and title.
Disabling editing of sum text field.
Fixing validation warnings and AdBanner on older ios'
Changing signing entity to work with iTunes Connect.
